| Method | Belongs to | When to use |
|--------|-----------|-------------|
| `createAgentSession({ customTools })` | Options object | Register tools from SDK code |
| `defineTool()` | Standalone helper | Typed tool definition for arrays |
| `pi.registerTool()` | `ExtensionAPI` | Inside extension factories |
| `session.setActiveToolsByName()` | `AgentSession` | Enable/disable already-registered tools |
| `session.getToolDefinition()` | `AgentSession` | Look up a registered tool |

