Run orchestrator             feed-state.test.ts  
(with new revamp)              → unit test each function:
                                  completeCurrentStep()
                                  addSubstep()
                                  renderActivityFeed()
                                  planSteps handler
                                  advanceStep handler
                                → 100% deterministic

Run orchestrator             snapshot.test.ts
                              → renderActivityFeed(feed)
                              → jest/vitest snapshot
                              → catches visual regressions
```

