`/private/tmp/orchestrator-timeline-mqfumcmmqgasn0.json` — use it as the first test fixture. Replay the old (broken) behavior, then run the same events through the new (revamped) code. The output should be **monotonic** (no 3/6 ghost state) instead of cycling.

