|------|--------|
| `subagent-runner.ts` | Register `reportFinding` tool + add to `allTools` array |
| `activity-feed.ts` | Add back `isReport` rendering for completed substeps (only the `✓ Report:` prefix part) |
| `specialists.ts` | Add `reportFinding()` to system prompt instructions |

Want me to implement?

